        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="gear-info">
        <div class="gear-type">Preamp / EQ</div>
        <h2>HA73-EQX2</h2>
        <p>Dual-channel Neve 1073-style preamp with three-band EQ. The front end of both the vocal and guitar chains. Class A transformer-coupled gain stage.</p>
        <div class="gear-spec">Ch A: Vocal (SM7B, gain knob 35)<br>Ch B: Guitar return (post amp sim)<br>Signal: Ch1/Ch2 → Out 1/2 → HA73 → WA76 → ...</div>
      </div>
    </a>

