        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="gear-info">
        <div class="gear-type">Compressor</div>
        <h2>WA76-D2</h2>
        <p>Dual 1176-style FET compressor. Fast attack, program-dependent release. Ratio at 4:1 for both vocal and guitar channels. Always in the chain.</p>
        <div class="gear-spec">Ch A: Vocal (post HA73 A)<br>Ch B: Guitar (post HA73 B)<br>Signal: HA73 → WA76 → Distressor/Opto</div>
      </div>
    </a>

