        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="gear-info">
        <div class="gear-type">Digital Mixer</div>
        <h2>Wing Rack</h2>
        <p>48 channels, 16 buses, 8 matrices, 16 FX slots. OSC-controlled at 192.168.2.2. Handles all routing, monitoring, amp sims, and FX processing.</p>
        <div class="gear-spec">40 inputs / 24 outputs / 48kHz<br>USB 1–6: recording to Logic<br>Amp sims: DELUXE, ANGEL, RACKAMP</div>
